no.motif.iter

Class PreparedIterable<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • no.motif.iter.CollectingIterable<T>
      • no.motif.iter.PreparedIterable<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type of the elements in the iterable.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Appendable<T>, Elements<T>, Filterable<T>, Mappable<T>, Prependable<T>, Reducible<T>

    public class PreparedIterable<T>
extends CollectingIterable<T>
implements Iterable<T>, Elements<T>
    This class wraps an arbitrary Iterable and provides access to various operations to view and/or transform the wrapped iterable.
